INSTALL
=-----=

For detailed installation instructions please see the Gizmo Daemon web 
site.

The basics are as follows:

tar jxvf gizmod-X.x.tar.bz2
mkdir build
cd build
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr -DSYSCONF_INSTALL_DIR=/etc ../gizmod-X.x
make
sudo make install

